233
00:35:03,982 --> 00:35:06,314
It seemed to go perfectly,
but then...

234
00:35:06,351 --> 00:35:08,819
he started to feel nauseous
on the way back.

235
00:35:08,853 --> 00:35:11,185
I'm sure it's a concussion.

236
00:35:11,222 --> 00:35:14,680
Well, we're familiar enough
with that then, aren't we?

237
00:36:00,772 --> 00:36:02,364
Seagrave.

238
