crash with you.

241
00:36:25,730 --> 00:36:27,129
We could...

242
00:36:29,100 --> 00:36:32,592
We could do the...
the decapitation.

243
00:36:34,372 --> 00:36:37,364
The head embedded
in the windshield.

244
00:36:37,408 --> 00:36:40,809
The world record is
a whopping forty-two pounds.

245
00:36:40,845 --> 00:36:43,336
And the dead dog thing,
you know?

246
00:36:48,052 --> 00:36:50,520
You know, the Chihuahua
in the back seat?

247
00:36:50,555 --> 00:36:52,546
I got it all worked out.

248
00:36:58,062 --> 00:37:00,053
I'll be ready, Vaughan.

249
00:37:00,098 --> 00:37:02,692
I want really big tits.

250
00:37:04,702 --> 00:37:06,192
Out to here.

251
00:37:08,540 --> 00:37:10,906
So the audience can see 'em
get all cut up...

252
00:37:10,942 --> 00:37:13,274
and crushed on the dashboard.

253
00:37:17,882 --> 00:37:20,043
Yeah, we'll do that.

254
00:37:20,084 --> 00:37:22,109
Ballard...

255
00:37:22,153 --> 00:37:24,178
I need your help.

256
00:37:49,514 --> 00:37:51,311
Do you live here with Seagrave?

257
00:37:51,349 --> 00:37:54,147
No. I live in my car.
This is my workshop.

258
00:38:14,305 --> 00:38:16,296
This is my new project.

259
00:38:38,329 --> 00:38:40,058
You recognize her?

260
00:38:41,833 --> 00:38:43,130
That's Gabrielle.

261
00:38:45,770 --> 00:38:47,328
That's her right outside
the door there.

262
00:39:36,154 --> 00:39:38,622
I thought you might be
missing these.

263
00:39:44,629 --> 00:39:45,618
Right.

264
00:39:50,201 --> 00:39:52,567
So here you are
